to make page content full screen:
html,body{height:100%;width:100%}
then in every part:divide

margin: top right bottom left;

to make a table in the middle of the screen:
write in the corresponsing class:vertical-align:middle

to change the body color for the whole text: 
<body text="green">
OR
writen in css:
body{color:white

css text-align:center
h1 {
    text-align: center;
}
